00:37:20,500 --> 00:37:22,510
If you tell him it's Kwon Jae Book, he'll know who I am.

494
00:37:22,510 --> 00:37:25,300
Are you Lawyer Kwon's father?

495
00:37:25,300 --> 00:37:28,100
Yes, how did you guess that so quickly?

496
00:37:28,100 --> 00:37:30,620
I just had a feeling.

497
00:37:30,620 --> 00:37:34,580
If you walk straight down that way, you'll get to his office. I'll take you there.

498
00:37:34,580 --> 00:37:37,000
No, it's okay.

499
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:39,760
I'll find it on my own.

500
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:44,540
Sending the judgment statements, complete.

501
00:37:49,970 --> 00:37:52,190
How can you follow me all the way here?

502
00:37:52,190 --> 00:37:54,610
I told you, I'm not Oh Yoon Seo!

503
00:37:59,340 --> 00:38:01,880
That's right, I am Oh Yoon Seo.

504
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:05,060
- Do you feel refreshed now?
 - What?

505
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:10,340
You said that you're my fan.  I'm asking if you feel refreshed now that you've attacked and cornered me like this.

506
00:38:10,340 --> 00:38:14,390
How in the world did you know that I work here?

507
00:38:14,390 --> 00:38:18,440
How much do you know about me?

508
00:38:27,460 --> 00:38:30,590
Look here, young lady. It seems like you've been misunderstanding something since earlier,

509
00:38:30,590 --> 00:38:32,590
but I'm not your fan.

510
00:38:32,590 --> 00:38:35,790
I just picked this pen up and was trying to give it back to you.
  ("Pen" and "fan" sound very similar in Korean) 

511
00:38:35,790 --> 00:38:36,580
What?

512
00:38:36,580 --> 00:38:42,110
And I wasn't following you. I came because I had something to say to my son.

513
00:38:42,110 --> 00:38:45,440
What do you mean, you had something to say to your son?

514
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:48,970
Isn't this Lawyer Kwon Jeong Rok's office?

515
00:38:49,550 --> 00:38:52,090
- That's right.
 - That's what I'm saying.

516
00:38:52,090 --> 00:38:55,790
I'm telling you that I came to meet Lawyer Kwon Jeong Rok, my son.

517
00:38:55,790 --> 00:38:59,880
So you're Lawyer Kwon Jeong Rok's...

518
00:39:03,190 --> 00:39:04,980
Father?!

519
00:39:07,020 --> 00:39:09,360
Hello, Father! Oh, my.

520
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:17,350
Father.

521
00:39:29,930 --> 00:39:32,750
This is killing me, seriously.

522
00:39:32,750 --> 00:39:36,380
How could I make such a mistake toward Mr. Lawyer's father?

523
00:39:49,970 --> 00:39:51,930
What brings you here?

524
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:56,810
Make sure you dress warmly.

525
00:39:56,810 --> 00:40:00,960
Why is your throat all out in the open? You'll catch a cold like that.

526
00:40:02,260 --> 00:40:06,990
I'm managing my condition very well so that I won't catch a cold.

527
00:40:06,990 --> 00:40:09,540
And call your mom often.

528
00:40:09,540 --> 00:40:11,400
That's something that I'm worrying about in my own way.

529
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:15,020
You know it. You could just do as I say once.

530
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:17,560
You won't let me have the last word just once.

531
00:40:22,640 --> 00:40:25,540
By the way, the more I think about it, the more dumbfounded I feel.

532
00:40:25,540 --> 00:40:29,050
She misunderstood that I was following her around.

533
00:40:30,160 --> 00:40:32,840
Your secretary is an impetuous person.

534
00:40:32,840 --> 00:40:35,530
It's truly worrisome.

535
00:40:36,080 --> 00:40:39,660
Everyone misunderstands and makes mistakes.

536
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:48,690
Did that secretary also do this?

537
00:40:50,240 --> 00:40:52,360
She's not coloring some coloring book.

538
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:54,800
With the time that she took to color this,

539
00:40:54,800 --> 00:40:57,790
she could have taken care of another work task.

540
00:40:57,790 --> 00:40:59,720
She completes the work that I assign her very well.

541
00:40:59,720 --> 00:41:03,540
How have I been thinking wrong?

542
00:41:03,540 --> 00:41:06,470
Look at her outfit. Is that something that a worker wears?

543
00:41:06,470 --> 00:41:09,970
Isn't it prejudiced to judge someone based on their outward appearance?

544
00:41:09,970 --> 00:41:11,830
Even so, once you've seen one, you've seen them all.

545
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:16,180
Father. Tell me why you came here.

546
00:41:16,180 --> 00:41:19,980
Your father has come to see his son. Does there really have to be a reason?

547
00:41:19,980 --> 00:41:22,330
This is my place of work.

548
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:24,990
Because you came looking for me during my work hours,

549
00:41:24,990 --> 00:41:27,160
I thought that you had an urgent reason.

550
00:41:27,160 --> 00:41:28,890
Fine, I get it!

551
00:41:28,890 --> 00:41:32,570
I'm sorry I came and disturbed your precious work time.

552
00:41:32,570 --> 00:41:35,470
I should go and take care of my work, too.

553
00:41:39,550 --> 00:41:43,840
Excuse me, Father. A cup of coffee... Goodbye.

554
00:41:51,860 --> 00:41:55,130
Why did Father just leave?

555
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:57,510
He didn't even have any coffee.

556
00:41:58,630 --> 00:42:02,000
Did you two fight?

557
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:04,470
No way... Was it because of me?

558
00:42:05,070 --> 00:42:08,900
No, that's not it. Don't worry about it.

559
00:42:08,900 --> 00:42:11,970
I don't think that's not what happened.

560
00:42:13,480 --> 00:42:16,720
He was in a bad mood because of me, wasn't he?

561
00:42:16,720 --> 00:42:21,650
My father's personality doesn't mix well with mine, so there's trouble every time we meet.

562
00:42:21,650 --> 00:42:23,870
Though it's not something to be proud of.

563
00:42:23,870 --> 00:42:27,750
So you don't have to worry about him anymore.

564
00:42:35,940 --> 00:42:38,820
Let's put together all the documents we've prepared and indict him.

565
00:42:38,820 --> 00:42:40,680
So you've decided to arrest him!

566
00:42:40,680 --> 00:42:42,890
Then shall we go eat lunch?

567
00:42:42,890 --> 00:42:44,850
That sounds good! Let's go eat something good.

568
00:42:44,850 --> 00:42:48,740
You worked hard, so go and eat something delicious today.

569
00:42:48,740 --> 00:42:50,670
- Beef ribs? 
- Korean beef!

570
00:42:51,270 --> 00:42:54,340
- Let's do that.
- Yes, this is Prosecutor Kim Se Won's office.

571
00:42:54,960 --> 00:42:56,790
Yes, Section Chief.

572
00:42:58,620 --> 00:43:00,320
Sir?

573
00:43:09,740 --> 00:43:12,050
Why are you preparing for something unpleasant?

574
00:43:12,050 --> 00:43:14,780
How drastic is the news you're about to tell me?

575
00:43:16,570 --> 00:43:21,510
All right.  I'll get right to the point.

576
00:43:21,510 --> 00:43:25,560
About the case with Jeong Ji Ho. Hurry up and finish it.

577
00:43:29,230 --> 00:43:31,490
I want to do that more than anyone else, of course.

578
00:43:31,490 --> 00:43:34,880
So I'm raising my speed little by little.

579
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:37,120
Now that I've listened closely,

580
00:43:37,120 --> 00:43:39,640
Jeong Ji Ho is a gambler.

581
00:43:39,640 --> 00:43:43,860
The evidence is insufficient to prove he was involved in embezzlement or a slush fund.

582
00:43:43,860 --> 00:43:48,300
I think its correct that it is circumstantial evidence of the vice-president's personal corruption.

583
00:43:50,070 --> 00:43:52,120
Is that what's right,

584
00:43:52,120 --> 00:43:55,120
or do I have to make that what's right?

585
00:43:56,200 --> 00:44:01,160
Is this an order to you?

586
00:44:01,160 --> 00:44:01,990
What?

587
00:44:01,990 --> 00:44:05,990
Choi Yeon Soo, the lawyer leading the defense for Jeong Ji Ho is your brother-in-law.

588
00:44:05,990 --> 00:44:08,070
What's the big deal about that?

589
00:44:08,070 --> 00:44:11,300
The embezzlement is just the individual corruption of the vice-president.

590
00:44:11,300 --> 00:44:13,150
Section Chief!

591
00:44:14,600 --> 00:44:18,560
Section Chief, you remember what you said when I returned, don't you?

592
00:44:18,560 --> 00:44:21,660
You said that if it wasn't a lunatic like me,

593
00:44:21,660 --> 00:44:23,670
then it wouldn't be easy to take care of Jeong Ji Ho's case.

594
00:44:23,670 --> 00:44:25,830
I get what you're saying.

595
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:27,420
I'm really ashamed of this.

596
00:44:27,420 --> 00:44:30,980
But the obstacle is higher than I thought.

597
00:44:32,130 --> 00:44:34,120
It was difficult for you to come back.

598
00:44:34,120 --> 00:44:38,590
I'm doing this because I feel like you'll also be in danger if you continue.

599
00:45:04,240 --> 00:45:09,980
Mr. Lawyer, did you call your father and see if he made it back okay?

600
00:45:09,980 --> 00:45:13,170
I'm worried that he may not have been able

601
00:45:13,170 --> 00:45:16,020
to tell you what he came here to say because of me.

602
00:45:16,020 --> 00:45:19,290
That's not true. He came for no reason.

603
00:45:19,290 --> 00:45:21,690
That's not true. He definitely told me

604
00:45:21,690 --> 00:45:25,790
that he came because he had something to tell his son earlier.

605
00:45:25,790 --> 00:45:27,560
What?

606
00:45:31,170 --> 00:45:34,640
- I'll answer the phone.
 - Okay, then I'll...

607
00:45:38,390 --> 00:45:41,710
Yes, Mother. Just a little while ago, I—

608
00:45:44,510 --> 00:45:47,150
What? Father did?

609
00:45:47,150 --> 00:45:52,790
 Your father, because he revealed that the Deputy Mayor embezzled 2.7 billion won in construction funds, 

610
00:45:52,790 --> 00:45:57,080
 was suspended for three months for violating the Civil Service Act. 

611
00:45:57,080 --> 00:46:00,390
 Your father didn't say anything? 

612
00:46:00,390 --> 00:46:02,480
 He said that he was going to talk to you about it. 

613
00:46:02,500 --> 00:46:05,100
 Deputy Mayor Kim Joon Cheol must retract the unfair punishment 

614
00:46:16,640 --> 00:46:19,080
 Yuyang Municipal Building 

615
00:46:22,070 --> 00:46:24,130
I'm here.

616
00:46:25,260 --> 00:46:28,240
Why did you come here? How did you know?

617
00:46:28,240 --> 00:46:29,660
I heard from Mother.

618
00:46:29,660 --> 00:46:32,930
Your mom did something useless again.

619
00:46:32,930 --> 00:46:34,460
You must be busy. Go ahead and leave.

620
00:46:34,460 --> 00:46:37,680
Let's go somewhere and have a cup of coffee.

621
00:46:37,680 --> 00:46:40,550
Does it look like it's time for me to drink coffee?

622
00:46:41,380 --> 00:46:45,640
Even if you're  going to protest, do it while taking care of your body.

623
00:46:46,980 --> 00:46:50,770
 Yuyang Municipal Office 

624
00:46:53,630 --> 00:46:56,060
Wait, that rascal!

625
00:47:01,190 --> 00:47:03,630
There's nothing for you to sigh about.

626
00:47:03,630 --> 00:47:07,550
Rather than suffering because I was suspended, I'm thinking it was a fortunate thing.

627
00:47:07,550 --> 00:47:08,550
What do you mean by that?

628
00:47:08,550 --> 00:47:11,840
Despite my revelation of the wrongdoing, nothing has changed.

629
00:47:11,840 --> 00:47:14,950
Everyone's attitude is to take it easy on the job.

630
00:47:14,950 --> 00:47:18,130
But they suspended me from work for three months

631
00:47:18,130 --> 00:47:22,060
so I gained a reason to protest.

632
00:47:22,060 --> 00:47:27,560
Isn't this perhaps a better way to let the world know about it?

633
00:47:30,600 --> 00:47:33,600
You submitted an appeal petition, right?

634
00:47:33,600 --> 00:47:35,200
When is your court hearing?

635
00:47:35,200 --> 00:47:37,300
Tomorrow.

636
00:47:37,360 --> 00:47:40,570
And if they decide to discipline you?

637
00:47:40,570 --> 00:47:43,290
Then I'll have to file a lawsuit to cancel the disciplinary action.

638
00:47:43,290 --> 00:47:46,020
Is that why you came to the law firm earlier?

639
00:47:47,630 --> 00:47:51,830
So you could ask me to be your lawyer if you ended up getting into a lawsuit?

640
00:47:55,320 --> 00:47:59,210
Then you should have just said that from the start.

641
00:47:59,210 --> 00:48:03,540
Are you offering to take my side so I could say that you did?

642
00:48:03,540 --> 00:48:08,450
Still, did you have to just leave? You just make me into the bad son.

643
00:48:19,260 --> 00:48:22,520
So that's what happened.

644
00:48:23,560 --> 00:48:25,790
He must have already been having a difficult time,

645
00:48:25,830 --> 00:48:29,050
and, of all things, I just had to make a mistake like this.

646
00:48:31,550 --> 00:48:34,160
Don't worry too much about it. It's not that big a deal.

647
00:48:34,160 --> 00:48:37,840
Even if he does get disciplinary action, it'll end when he files the lawsuit to cancel it.

648
00:48:37,840 --> 00:48:40,340
I'll turn things back to how they're supposed to be no matter what it takes,

649
00:48:40,390 --> 00:48:43,280
so you don't have to worry about it anymore.

650
00:48:45,640 --> 00:48:47,570
I'm telling you, it's okay.

651
00:48:47,570 --> 00:48:51,460
No, that's it's own matter.

652
00:48:51,460 --> 00:48:56,410
But I'm worried that I may have gotten on his bad side.

653
00:48:56,410 --> 00:49:02,150
Anyway, I'm sure he's concerned that he is meeting a celebrity who unfortunately has experienced a lot of criticism.

654
00:49:02,830 --> 00:49:05,970
I ruined his first impression of me like that.

655
00:49:10,800 --> 00:49:13,230
There's nothing for you to be upset about.

656
00:49:14,200 --> 00:49:18,530
No one could dislike you after they find out what kind of person you are.

657
00:49:18,530 --> 00:49:22,350
Do you think you won various TV popularity awards for nothing?

658
00:49:29,280 --> 00:49:33,470
Ah, then is your father going to his court hearing alone tomorrow?

659
00:49:33,470 --> 00:49:37,140
Yes. Father will  talk about his principles

660
00:49:37,140 --> 00:49:39,590
and he will go there and hear the disposition of his discipline.

661
00:49:39,590 --> 00:49:42,350
So I don't think there's a need for me to attend.

662
00:49:43,470 --> 00:49:45,290
I see.

663
00:49:45,290 --> 00:49:50,640
Wait. Your father will probably be nervous if he goes in all alone.

664
00:49:54,190 --> 00:49:56,700
What? You're telling me to go to my father's hearing?

665
00:49:56,700 --> 00:50:00,390
No matter how I think about it, I think that your father will be really nervous if he goes by himself,

666
00:50:00,390 --> 00:50:05,410
so I think that it would be good for you as his son and a lawyer to attend.

667
00:50:05,450 --> 00:50:10,120
I cleared your morning schedule, so hurry and go.

668
00:50:10,120 --> 00:50:14,440
I'm thankful for the thought, but you're saying that because you don't know my father very well.

669
00:50:14,440 --> 00:50:17,210
My father is not someone to get nervous over something like this.

670
00:50:17,210 --> 00:50:19,540
He's much more mentally strong than me.

671
00:50:19,540 --> 00:50:22,050
That's what you think, Mr. Lawyer.

672
00:50:22,050 --> 00:50:26,040
No matter how strong he may be, he's in an unfamiliar situation right now.

673
00:50:26,040 --> 00:50:28,430
He could be unusually nervous

674
00:50:28,430 --> 00:50:32,330
and you never know if he needs someone to lean on.

675
00:50:36,160 --> 00:50:40,720
Just go one time! Ah, seriously.

676
00:50:40,720 --> 00:50:46,890
It's because I feel so uneasy thinking that you two may have fought because of me.

677
00:50:46,920 --> 00:50:51,010
So please think of me and just go once. Okay?

678
00:50:51,010 --> 00:50:53,920
Yes, well.

679
00:50:53,960 --> 00:50:56,750
Then, head on!

680
00:50:57,890 --> 00:51:00,680
Ah. Here.

681
00:51:00,680 --> 00:51:03,830
Take this with you. It's a calming medicine.

682
00:51:03,830 --> 00:51:07,040
It's an old item that doesn't really suit my image,

683
00:51:07,080 --> 00:51:10,110
but it gets rid of nervousness when you drink it.

684
00:51:10,110 --> 00:51:12,940
Then, be careful on your way.

685
00:51:12,940 --> 00:51:16,790
Take off! Alright, let's go!

686
00:51:47,250 --> 00:51:50,420
I'm here.

687
00:51:50,420 --> 00:51:52,390
Why did you come?

688
00:51:54,370 --> 00:51:58,230
Because my appointment was canceled, so I just came.

689
00:51:58,240 --> 00:52:01,590
You must have more free time than I thought.

690
00:52:03,860 --> 00:52:09,720
I've prepared a position statement so there shouldn't be any serious problems.

691
00:52:17,420 --> 00:52:20,130
Even if you possibly get disciplinary action and go with a lawsuit,

692
00:52:20,170 --> 00:52:22,590
I'm sure we will obtain a favorable decision,

693
00:52:22,630 --> 00:52:25,150
so don't worry too much.

694
00:52:26,890 --> 00:52:28,740
I'm not worried.

695
00:52:28,740 --> 00:52:31,280
Of course you should do that.

