Thank you for worrying about him.

714
00:54:12,140 --> 00:54:14,780
No, don't mention it.

715
00:54:14,820 --> 00:54:19,590
Comfort your father well. Don't pick at him for no reason.

716
00:54:19,590 --> 00:54:22,510
Buy him some delicious lunch so that he can regain his energy.

717
00:54:22,510 --> 00:54:24,770
And...

